Taxify OÃœ is an Estonian international transportation network company headquartered in Tallinn, Estonia. The company develops and operates the Taxify mobile application, which allows people to request a taxi or private driver from their smartphone. As of November 2017, Taxify operates in 20 countries and 30 cities in Europe, Africa, Middle East and Central America, mediating tens of millions of rides every year to over three million customers.
